00:01:22,930 --> 00:01:28,750
[Fall In Love]

15
00:01:28,750 --> 00:01:31,570
[Episode 16]

16
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:42,079
- What?
- They'll be there soon.

17
00:01:42,079 --> 00:01:44,210
Are they here to pick a bone with Zhixia?

18
00:01:44,210 --> 00:01:46,390
Attention, everyone. Come with me.

19
00:01:46,390 --> 00:01:48,610
Someone came here looking for trouble with Zhixia.

20
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,719
What are you doing here?

21
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:59,322
We don't welcome you here.

22
00:01:59,322 --> 00:02:01,832
A boy is not qualified to talk to me.

23
00:02:01,832 --> 00:02:03,850
Miss He.

24
00:02:06,820 --> 00:02:08,490
Sister.

25
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:12,449
What brings you to Aizhe?

26
00:02:12,450 --> 00:02:15,849
I'm not here to see you. Where's Fu Zeyi?

27
00:02:20,910 --> 00:02:22,960
Hello, Miss He.

28
00:02:24,536 --> 00:02:27,289
Miss Jing, I'm here to discuss something about the Fu Group.

29
00:02:27,289 --> 00:02:30,399
You can leave now.

30
00:02:30,399 --> 00:02:34,844
If Director Fu says he doesn't need me, he will ask me to leave.

31
00:02:34,844 --> 00:02:36,770
Am I right, Director Fu?

32
00:02:36,770 --> 00:02:39,850
Yes. Zhixia is one of us.

33
00:02:39,850 --> 00:02:42,529
All right, then I won't waste time.

34
00:02:42,529 --> 00:02:45,520
The Fu Group stole my designs.

35
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:49,840
What are you going to do about this?

36
00:02:50,643 --> 00:02:53,905
Aren't the Fu Group and Helai Jewelry strategic partners?

37
00:02:53,905 --> 00:02:55,649
I'm an independent designer.

38
00:02:55,650 --> 00:03:00,583
I still have proprietary rights over the new product designs of the furniture promoted at the press conference.

39
00:03:00,583 --> 00:03:04,150
If you want to use my designs, please pay the copyright fee

40
00:03:04,150 --> 00:03:08,300
or else it's plagiarism.

41
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:09,720
All right.

42
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:12,669
Tell me, how much are the copyright fees?

43
00:03:12,669 --> 00:03:14,700
Not much.

44
00:03:14,700 --> 00:03:16,409
- Just 500 million yuan ($71,8 million).
- Say that again?

45
00:03:16,409 --> 00:03:18,540
That's daylight robbery.

46
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:24,299
I know an artist's work deserves some respect,

47
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:26,220
but 500 million yuan is outrageous.

48
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:28,410
Fine, you can choose not to pay.

49
00:03:28,410 --> 00:03:30,570
Then apologize to me.

50
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:32,590
Okay.

51
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:35,160
I'm willing to apologize if I did something wrong.

52
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:36,739
Your apology isn't sincere at all.

53
00:03:36,739 --> 00:03:39,150
How do you want me to apologize?

54
00:03:40,219 --> 00:03:45,178
The day we announced the marriage alliance for the two enterprises, you left in front of everyone.

55
00:03:45,178 --> 00:03:48,149
Let's do it on a similar occasion

56
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,440
where you kneel and apologize in front of everyone.

57
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:55,190
How about we do it on the day of the press conference?

58
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:58,490
Are you done talking?

59
00:03:58,490 --> 00:04:00,090
Then you can leave now.

60
00:04:00,090 --> 00:04:02,030
See yourself out.

61
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:27,090
He Bei'er,

62
00:04:31,780 --> 00:04:33,370
I've made up my mind.

63
00:04:33,370 --> 00:04:34,770
I'll pay the fees.

64
00:04:34,770 --> 00:04:38,550
But you need to give me time to raise 500 million yuan.

65
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:42,190
All right. We'll sign the contract at the same time tomorrow.

66
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:44,859
All right. I'll see you tomorrow.

67
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:05,750
We only have one day. Can we raise this much money in such a short time?

68
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:07,120
Of course not.

69
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:09,610
Why did you tell me to agree to pay the fees?

70
00:05:09,610 --> 00:05:12,530
We need time to think of a solution.

71
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:17,910
If it was Fu Zeyi, I think he'd do the same.

72
00:05:21,967 --> 00:05:24,777
He probably left something important.

73
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,820
But I don't know the password to his computer.

74
00:05:28,820 --> 00:05:30,610
Password?

75
00:05:30,610 --> 00:05:33,630
It must be related to someone important.

76
00:05:34,453 --> 00:05:35,600
[Fu Zeyi]

77
00:05:37,403 --> 00:05:38,675
[Incorrect password. Please try again.]

78
00:05:40,482 --> 00:05:43,542
That's awkward. I can't believe it's not my date of birth.

79
00:05:43,542 --> 00:05:47,510
So tell me who's the most important person to him.

80
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:50,340
Let me try again.

81
00:05:50,340 --> 00:05:53,550
You can go and look for any important documents or contracts.

82
00:05:53,550 --> 00:05:55,210
Okay.

83
00:05:56,487 --> 00:05:59,997
I don't believe it. Let me try again.

84
00:05:59,997 --> 00:06:03,700
It must be my name if it's not my date of birth.

85
00:06:03,700 --> 00:06:04,920
[Incorrect password. Please try again.]

86
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:07,515
It's not my name either.

87
00:06:08,161 --> 00:06:09,750
[Second Uncle]

88
00:06:11,100 --> 00:06:12,790
It's Second Uncle.

89
00:06:12,790 --> 00:06:15,600
- Answer it.
- Answer it?

90
00:06:19,940 --> 00:06:22,350
Hello, Second Uncle. What can I do for you?

91
00:06:22,350 --> 00:06:26,626
Zeyi, are you really planning on compensating a fee of 500 million yuan?

92
00:06:26,626 --> 00:06:28,019
Do you have any better ideas?

93
00:06:28,020 --> 00:06:32,819
You see, He Bei'er is just aiming at you.

94
00:06:32,819 --> 00:06:37,299
If you refuse to kneel, how about you take the blame and resign?

95
00:06:37,299 --> 00:06:40,870
The matter won't affect the Fu Group this way.

96
00:06:42,980 --> 00:06:45,519
He's really well-informed.

97
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:47,850
I only mentioned the compensation.

98
00:06:47,850 --> 00:06:50,170
I never said anything about kneeling.

99
00:06:52,940 --> 00:06:54,490
Mr. Fu...

100
00:06:55,780 --> 00:06:57,660
Second Uncle, you sure are well-informed.

101
00:06:57,660 --> 00:07:00,779
I only mentioned the compensation. I never said anything about kneeling.

102
00:07:00,779 --> 00:07:02,080
You see...

103
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:06,459
When I met He Bei'er to plead for you, she insisted that you kneel.

104
00:07:06,459 --> 00:07:09,019
She's not going to let it go. What do you want me to do? I've tried to help you out.

105
00:07:09,019 --> 00:07:14,030
Since you can't help, you can stay out of this now.

106
00:07:14,987 --> 00:07:19,830
Since you can't help, you can stay out of this now.

107
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:21,573
Then take it as me meddling in your affairs.

108
00:07:21,573 --> 00:07:23,882
You can explain it to the shareholders when the time comes.

109
00:07:23,882 --> 00:07:27,552
You caused this problem yourself anyway.

110
00:07:27,552 --> 00:07:29,310
All right.

111
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,910
Is he still adamant about not apologizing?

112
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,790
Could it be that

113
00:07:43,790 --> 00:07:45,570
he has something else up his sleeves?

114
00:07:45,570 --> 00:07:49,470
My nephew is not an easy opponent.

115
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:55,082
What if we can't find that thing?

116
00:07:56,000 --> 00:08:00,570
We have no choice. Unless Fu Zeyi comes back.

117
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:03,180
Take a look at this.

118
00:08:03,180 --> 00:08:05,030
Hello, Director Fu.

119
00:08:05,030 --> 00:08:07,890
- Hello, Director Fu.
- Hello, Director Fu.

120
00:08:11,060 --> 00:08:12,410
- Hello, Director Fu.
- Hello, Director Fu.

121
00:08:12,410 --> 00:08:14,113
- Hello, Director Fu.
- Hello, Director Fu.

122
00:08:14,114 --> 00:08:15,175
[Fu Group]

123
00:08:17,990 --> 00:08:20,649
I feel so bad for Sister Ai Xin.

124
00:08:20,650 --> 00:08:24,620
She just finished her vacation. Now, she has to deal with such a problem.

125
00:08:24,620 --> 00:08:30,309
Are we going to pack and leave with Director Fu because of this 500 million yuan compensation?

126
00:08:30,309 --> 00:08:34,709
How about we meet and kneel in front of Director Fu? Then we tell him that kneeling is not a big deal.

127
00:08:34,709 --> 00:08:36,900
What nonsense are you talking about?

128
00:08:48,610 --> 00:08:51,349
Hello, Miss He. Director Fu has been waiting for you.

129
00:08:51,349 --> 00:08:53,020
This way, please.

130
00:08:59,230 --> 00:09:03,320
This is the draft of the contract. Please take a look at it.

131
00:09:09,490 --> 00:09:12,290
Fu Zeyi, do you still have the cheek to stay with Fu Group,

132
00:09:12,290 --> 00:09:14,960
even if you pay the 500 million yuan compensation?

133
00:09:14,969 --> 00:09:17,487
Who says I'm going to pay the compensation?

134
00:09:17,487 --> 00:09:20,620
Does that mean you agreed to kneel?

135
00:09:20,620 --> 00:09:22,924
He's going to kneel.

136
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:27,440
What's this?

137
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:30,480
These are the copyrights I've obtained.

138
00:09:33,270 --> 00:09:36,269
I'm sure you're familiar with the names on the list.

139
00:09:36,269 --> 00:09:39,490
The designs had been revised several times. And the original designs don't belong to you.

140
00:09:39,490 --> 00:09:43,660
I've obtained the copyrights of all the designers except for yours.

141
00:09:45,970 --> 00:09:49,440
Fu Zeyi, how dare you threaten me.

142
00:09:51,350 --> 00:09:53,170
It must be hard on you these days.

143
00:09:53,170 --> 00:09:56,620
I'll pay you 100,000 yuan ($14,300) for your hard work.

144
00:09:56,629 --> 00:09:58,390
I've paid for these copyrights.

145
00:09:58,390 --> 00:10:01,740
You bribed them. Do you have any professional ethics at all?

146
00:10:03,310 --> 00:10:05,040
Listen here.

147
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:09,180
I don't need to be ethical when dealing with someone unethical like you.

148
00:10:09,180 --> 00:10:10,660
You...

149
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:14,880
You're done with the Fu Group.

150
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:17,249
But not with the rest.

151
00:10:17,250 --> 00:10:19,080
What do you mean?

152
00:10:20,230 --> 00:10:24,309
Do I need to tell you how you become a design influencer online?

153
00:10:25,230 --> 00:10:29,400
One of the people whose works you plagiarized is my friend.

154
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,369
He's going to sue you for plagiarizing.

155
00:10:31,369 --> 00:10:33,680
But he told me

156
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:38,630
he'd let the matter go, if I sent a video

157
00:10:38,630 --> 00:10:41,223
of you kneeling and apologizing to him.

158
00:10:41,223 --> 00:10:42,881
You can start now.

159
00:10:48,530 --> 00:10:51,000
Miss, be careful.

160
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:53,446
- Miss He.
- I can walk by myself.

161
00:11:01,170 --> 00:11:03,150
Miss.

162
00:11:08,570 --> 00:11:11,560
As expected of Director Fu.

163
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:15,749
You clearly don't know him well enough. He's just as brilliant as always.

164
00:11:16,430 --> 00:11:18,580
Don't you guys have anything to do?

165
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:20,240
Let's get back to work.

166
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:23,420
Take a look at this.

167
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:26,860
And this too.

168
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:38,150
I remember now.

169
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:39,730
[Eighteen hours ago]

170
00:11:39,730 --> 00:11:42,140
It's the summer solstice twenty years ago.

171
00:11:45,453 --> 00:11:46,350
[Fu Zeyi]

172
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:49,120
We're in.

173
00:11:49,970 --> 00:11:52,898
As far as I know, Fu Zeyi would always probe into new clients

174
00:11:52,898 --> 00:11:58,269
for any dark history before working with them to get something to be used against them as a leeway.

175
00:11:58,269 --> 00:12:01,729
It's the same for me, for Aizhe, for President Sheng, and for Yiju Home Furnishing.

176
00:12:01,729 --> 00:12:06,040
Helai Jewelry and He Bei'er won't be an exception either.

177
00:12:09,150 --> 00:12:11,090
[Three hours ago]

178
00:12:11,090 --> 00:12:14,180
Are these five contracts enough?

179
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:18,700
We still need something else.

180
00:12:24,290 --> 00:12:28,540
Later, you must play Fu Zeyi well.

181
00:12:30,293 --> 00:12:33,900
[Ethics is a tool used by the weak to tie down the strong.]

182
00:12:34,890 --> 00:12:39,900
"Ethics is a tool used by the weak to tie down the strong."

183
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:44,980
I'm not asking you to say it. You need to act this out.

184
00:12:44,980 --> 00:12:47,540
Act as Fu Zeyi?

185
00:13:00,710 --> 00:13:02,600
Ethics...

186
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:05,960
What is it again?

187
00:13:07,450 --> 00:13:12,080
Ethics is a tool used by the weak to tie down the strong.

188
00:13:15,030 --> 00:13:18,680
That's not the right tone. Watch me.

189
00:13:24,350 --> 00:13:27,580
Focus on your energy center and lift it up.

190
00:13:27,580 --> 00:13:29,540
Energy center?

191
00:13:33,150 --> 00:13:36,680
Put both hands in your pockets.

192
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:38,580
Be confident.

193
00:13:40,670 --> 00:13:42,440
Be confident.

194
00:13:45,090 --> 00:13:49,820
Look at the other person and say your lines.

195
00:13:53,030 --> 00:13:56,880
Ethics is a tool used by the weak to tie down the strong.

196
00:13:56,880 --> 00:13:58,680
Watch me.

197
00:13:58,680 --> 00:14:01,300
Bring your eyebrows together

198
00:14:03,130 --> 00:14:05,180
and say your lines.

199
00:14:05,180 --> 00:14:08,420
Ethics is a tool used by the weak to tie down the strong.

200
00:14:08,420 --> 00:14:13,489
Keep glaring at the person. Look into their eyes for three minutes.

201
00:14:13,489 --> 00:14:15,960
Don't blink.

202
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:20,689
You'll be able to suppress the other party with your domineering attitude.

203
00:14:21,570 --> 00:14:24,640
You'll look like Fu Zeyi this way.

204
00:14:43,164 --> 00:14:47,634
Director Fu, is there anything else I can help you with?

205
00:14:47,634 --> 00:14:50,229
Help me with the rest of the follow-ups.

206
00:15:17,370 --> 00:15:18,489
Keep a close watch.

207
00:15:18,489 --> 00:15:21,600
Report to me anytime.

208
00:15:23,789 --> 00:15:25,725
[Ethics is a tool used by the weak to tie down the strong.]

209
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:50,600
Why are you here?

210
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:54,200
You didn't answer when I called.

211
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:58,100
I was on a holiday for the past two days. I just came back.

212
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:02,120
I'm worried you might do something foolish at home.

213
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:05,400
I'm an adult. I won't do anything foolish.

214
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:09,200
Senior, I'm really worried about you.

215
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:12,500
Did that Fu make you like this?

216
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:18,400
If you're sad, you can just resign.

217
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:20,900
I'm indebted to him.

218
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:23,900
How can I leave that easily?

219
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:26,000
Indebted?

220
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:30,200
I just don't want you to work under Fu Zeyi.

221
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:33,500
Fu Zeyi has a mental problem.

222
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:36,400
What? Fu Zeyi?

223
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:41,500
I saw him talking to himself in front of the mirror.

224
00:16:42,410 --> 00:16:44,340
What else?

225
00:16:46,100 --> 00:16:50,700
Zhixia and I have seen him before at the psychiatric ward of North Olympic Hospital.

226
00:16:50,700 --> 00:16:53,080
I'm sure he has a secret.

227
00:17:01,680 --> 00:17:04,189
- Hello, Mr. Fu.
- Thank you.
[Reception]

228
00:17:07,870 --> 00:17:10,369
Hello, Director Fu. Are you here at this late hour?

229
00:17:10,369 --> 00:17:13,200
Yes. I brought Director Jing a late-night snack.

230
00:17:53,270 --> 00:17:55,420
How come there's a thief?

231
00:19:04,360 --> 00:19:08,230
Hello, hello? Security office?

232
00:19:08,230 --> 00:19:09,785
There's a thief.

233
00:19:09,785 --> 00:19:11,836
Send someone up here now.

234
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:32,800
Fu Zeyi, why did you only show up now?

235
00:19:32,800 --> 00:19:35,040
I was so scared.

236
00:19:46,750 --> 00:19:48,520
I'm sorry.

237
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:53,900
Why are you here at this late hour?

238
00:19:53,900 --> 00:19:56,080
I brought you food.

239
00:20:01,650 --> 00:20:04,800
Director Jing, Director Fu, are you all right?

240
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:06,660
We're all right.

241
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:19,800
I'm fine now.

242
00:20:19,800 --> 00:20:22,600
After catching the thief, the police will do some questioning.

243
00:20:22,600 --> 00:20:24,800
I need to go to the security office.

244
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:42,400
Fu Zeyi hasn't shown up for a long time.

245
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:44,620
I'm worried about him.

246
00:20:45,930 --> 00:20:49,680
This is my first time seeing an alternate personality seeking medical advice.

247
00:20:52,900 --> 00:20:55,700
I don't know how to treat you.

248
00:20:55,700 --> 00:21:01,100
But the only thing I can tell you is that it'll bring great harm to the body

249
00:21:01,100 --> 00:21:04,260
if the original personality goes into slumber for a long period.

250
00:21:11,170 --> 00:21:15,300
I've done my best from a medical perspective.

251
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:24,609
Fu Zeyi is my best friend.

252
00:21:24,609 --> 00:21:26,960
You have to cooperate with me,

253
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:31,360
accept my treatment, and take the initiative to leave.

254
00:21:31,990 --> 00:21:34,120
Only then will he return.

255
00:21:36,110 --> 00:21:38,160
Please let him go.

256
00:21:50,670 --> 00:21:52,760
I understand.

257
00:21:56,270 --> 00:21:58,780
Please give me some time.

258
00:22:27,870 --> 00:22:31,460
So Fu Zeyi is sick.

259
00:22:34,770 --> 00:22:36,760
You did well.

260
00:22:43,890 --> 00:22:45,090
[Aizhe Hotel]

261
00:22:45,090 --> 00:22:47,549
Sister, how did you turn this hopeless situation around?

262
00:22:47,549 --> 00:22:49,440
Tell me about it.

263
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:57,400
We pretended that we'd pay the 500 million yuan compensation to gain one day.

264
00:22:57,400 --> 00:23:00,600
After that, the smart old me found the authorization contracts

265
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:05,600
and authorized manuscripts of other designers on his computer.

266
00:23:05,600 --> 00:23:06,800
And then, checkmate.

267
00:23:06,800 --> 00:23:10,700
Sister, that's too unethical.

268
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:16,600
Ethics is a tool used by the weak to tie down the strong.

269
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:21,000
Why are you becoming like Fu Zeyi?

270
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:23,243
I'm not.

271
00:23:28,370 --> 00:23:30,160
Come in.

272
00:23:32,390 --> 00:23:34,929
Miss Jing, I need to talk to you in private.

273
00:23:34,929 --> 00:23:36,740
Sure.

274
00:23:43,300 --> 00:23:44,700
My girlfriend gave this to me.

275
00:23:44,700 --> 00:23:47,500
When is Fu Zeyi coming back?

276
00:23:47,500 --> 00:23:50,900
His alternate personality, Lin, has been present for a long time

277
00:23:50,900 --> 00:23:54,000
while the original personality, Fu Zeyi, has been in slumber.

278
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:55,640
Thank you.

279
00:24:01,300 --> 00:24:05,800
This means that Fu Zeyi's body can't support two personalities.
[Office]

280
00:24:05,800 --> 00:24:10,270
So I hope you can help me persuade Lin to leave.

281
00:24:10,270 --> 00:24:13,489
Are you saying that only one of them, Fu Zeyi or Lin,

282
00:24:13,489 --> 00:24:15,089
can survive?

283
00:24:15,100 --> 00:24:18,600
You can put it that way. After all, the body belongs to Fu Zeyi.

284
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:21,100
Lin is just his alternate personality.

285
00:24:21,100 --> 00:24:26,600
I'm sure you know who's more important, Miss Jing.

286
00:24:30,250 --> 00:24:32,042
I...

287
00:24:33,290 --> 00:24:35,300
I'll talk to Lin.

288
00:24:36,080 --> 00:24:38,299
Only you can persuade him to leave now.

289
00:24:38,300 --> 00:24:41,400
A'Yi's health is not looking good.

290
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:44,000
Don't worry. I know what to do.

291
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:45,560
Okay.

292
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:51,669
So no one wants me anymore.

293
00:25:09,460 --> 00:25:12,999
I'm sending food out of my concern as her friend.

294
00:25:12,999 --> 00:25:16,610
There's no reason for her to refuse, right?

295
00:25:21,900 --> 00:25:23,900
Zhang Xiaoyang.

296
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:26,670
Are you here to see Ai Xin?

297
00:25:26,670 --> 00:25:28,700
Keep it down. Don't tell her.

298
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:30,519
I want to give her a surprise.

299
00:25:30,519 --> 00:25:33,400
You can go to the back door of Ai Xin's office if you go around this way.

300
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:35,099
You'll definitely surprise her.

301
00:25:35,100 --> 00:25:36,600
You can read my mind.

302
00:25:36,600 --> 00:25:38,470
Go for it.

303
00:25:52,800 --> 00:25:55,600
I've been keeping an eye on his movements lately.

304
00:25:55,600 --> 00:26:00,000
Are there any new findings other than what you've reported to me before?

305
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:03,079
Other than the unusual situations I reported earlier,

306
00:26:03,079 --> 00:26:05,700
I've also obtained his medical record.

307
00:26:05,700 --> 00:26:11,500
He indeed visits the North Olympic Hospital frequently and keeps in touch with Dr. Mo.

308
00:26:11,500 --> 00:26:16,650
He's a famous psychiatrist from abroad called Mo Ziqi.

309
00:26:18,850 --> 00:26:20,739
[Medical Record]

310
00:26:20,739 --> 00:26:24,890
Dissociative... Identity Disorder.

311
00:26:25,900 --> 00:26:28,100
Interesting.

312
00:26:28,100 --> 00:26:30,100
You did well.

313
00:26:30,100 --> 00:26:32,700
My effort of nurturing you all these years didn't go to waste.

314
00:26:32,700 --> 00:26:36,500
You're the most reliable at a critical moment.

315
00:26:40,900 --> 00:26:42,770
Uncle Fu,

316
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:50,210
I want to resign.

317
00:26:55,100 --> 00:26:58,500
I know you're exhausted.

318
00:26:58,500 --> 00:27:02,700
We'll talk about this some other time.

319
00:27:31,580 --> 00:27:33,430
Senior.

320
00:27:39,140 --> 00:27:41,310
Why are you here?

321
00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:51,900
So you're the spy Fu Shengrong planted next to Fu Zeyi.

322
00:27:51,900 --> 00:27:54,000
Did you hear everything?

323
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:56,510
Aren't you going to explain?

324
00:27:57,740 --> 00:28:00,599
Congratulations on graduating smoothly.

325
00:28:00,599 --> 00:28:03,879
Uncle Fu, thank you for sponsoring my studies.

326
00:28:03,879 --> 00:28:07,400
So? Have you found a job yet?

327
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:09,210
Not yet.

328
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:13,500
Why don't you come and help me out then?

329
00:28:14,723 --> 00:28:17,747
[Ai Xin, Resume]

330
00:28:17,747 --> 00:28:20,379
[Fanmu Home Furnishing Employee Agreement]

331
00:28:20,379 --> 00:28:24,300
This person is my biggest competitor in the Fu Group.

332
00:28:24,300 --> 00:28:29,400
After this, you must find ways to stay next to him.

333
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:35,410
All right.

334
00:28:36,300 --> 00:28:38,200
I have nothing to explain.

335
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:42,100
So you had trouble sleeping because of this?

336
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:44,600
You feel guilty.

337
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:48,800
Is that the same person you were on the phone with when you were with me the other day?

338
00:28:50,700 --> 00:28:52,800
Also,

339
00:28:52,800 --> 00:28:57,300
is this also the reason you can't be with me?

340
00:28:57,300 --> 00:29:00,090
I'm sorry. I have nothing to say.

341
00:29:01,300 --> 00:29:06,200
The senior I knew was kind and beautiful.

342
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:08,430
She was smart and competent.

343
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:12,950
She got scholarships every year.

344
00:29:13,820 --> 00:29:16,190
In every school event,

345
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:21,800
she was always the center of attention as long as she participated.

346
00:29:21,800 --> 00:29:27,200
There was also a boy who liked her for six years.

347
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:30,250
She would never be like this.

