♫  It seems like I've locked my heart away as the memory lingers  ♫

352
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:37,100
♫  If I decide to be brave this time  ♫

353
00:30:37,100 --> 00:30:43,495
♫  Then I'll hold your hands till eternity  ♫

