00:30:44,560 --> 00:30:51,654
♫  The moment we found the emotions we'd lost,  ♫

355
00:30:51,654 --> 00:30:57,785
♫  we will overcome those lonely moments little by little  ♫

356
00:31:02,050 --> 00:31:05,550
♫  If you were by my side  ♫

357
00:31:05,550 --> 00:31:10,280
♫  No matter how many promises we've broken  ♫

358
00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:13,534
♫  There's nothing I'm not willing to do  ♫

359
00:31:13,534 --> 00:31:17,084
♫  in order to have a simple and ordinary life with you  ♫

360
00:31:17,084 --> 00:31:20,530
♫  If you were by my side  ♫

361
00:31:20,530 --> 00:31:27,100
♫  All my regrets will be blown away by the wind  ♫

362
00:31:27,100 --> 00:31:33,500
♫  I only want you to be with me every second, every minute  ♫
